text: Dionis Vodnyev (born 12 March 1971) is a Kazakhstani ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Unified Team Category:Ski jumpers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Almaty
